articles.title: Over a dozen vaccinated doctors dead as Indonesia's virus cases surge - New Straits Times
articles.description: JAKARTA: Over a dozen fully vaccinated doctors have died of Covid-19 in Indonesia, a medical association said Friday, as the Southeast Asian country battles a rash of severe cases in inoculated medical workers and highly infectious new virus strains.
